Different methods of OAuth Conection:
1) Authorization Code
    Prepare Web URL: https://{Domain_Url}/services/oauth2/authorize?client_id={client_Id}&redirect_uri={callback_Url}&response_type=code
    Url in PostMan: https://{Domain_Url}/services/oauth2/token?grant_type=authorization_code&code={Copied_Code_From_Web}&client_id={client_Id}&client_secret={client_Secret}&redirect_uri={callback_Url}
    Will get access Token along with instance url now.

2) Implicit Code
    Prepare Web URL: https://{Domain_Url}/services/oauth2/authorize?client_id={client_Id}&redirect_uri={callback_Url}&response_type=token
    Will get web url with access token and instance.

3) Refresh Token
    Prepare Web URL: https://{Domain_Url}/services/oauth2/authorize?client_id={client_Id}&redirect_uri={callback_Url}&response_type=code
    Url in PostMan: https://{Domain_Url}/services/oauth2/token?grant_type=refresh_token&client_id={client_Id}&client_secret={client_Secret}&refresh_token={refresh_token}
    Will get access Token along with instance url now.

4) Client Credentials
    Url in PostMan: https://{Domain_Url}/services/oauth2/token?grant_type=client_credentials&client_id={client_Id}&client_secret={client_Secret}
    Will get access Token along with instance url now.
